                <h1>Market Potential and Strategy </h1>
                <p class="col-md-10">
                    2020 was a challenging year for both Georgia and the whole world. This year greatly impacted technology and helped digital technologies and mobile applications to develop faster. However, it must be said, that smartphones take up a huge amount of people’s lives and it is necessary to pay more attention to the real world. INSTINCTY is a combination of these two opinions. By using technology it allows us to create profiles to show to society the desired side of us, but it also helps us to go outside and get useful information just by moving.
Everyone needs a technological innovation that makes life easier and considering the pandemic, helps create a healthier environment.
By avoiding unnecessary communication we lower the risks of spreading the virus, but also lose new chances and opportunities. INSTINCTY helps us to maintain those changes and opportunities.
Main commercialization targets are companies, shopping centers, and restaurants. INSTINCTY knows where customers are and what they need. INSTINCTY allows partner companies to send offers to users by being close to the location and while being close to the locations of competitor companies, offers them better conditions or discounts. The target audience of this strategy is users looking at products they have decided to buy. The same strategy can work at gas stations and restaurants.
The platform will have interesting games that will help motivate users to use INSTINCTY.
Mentioned features are already built into the platform and ready to be used. Our legal company, data protection policy, and rules have already been agreed with Apple, so INSTINCTY by CLEVER LLC can be found on both App Store and Play store. Our servers are located in Germany. A specific code that automatically sorts user information and sends them offers has already been written, in accordance with Georgian legislation. In conclusion, all rights are reserved.
                </p>
