                        INSTINCTY does not have direct competitors, but the combination of popular social media and meeting platforms can be seen as its indirect competitors. For example, Tinder and Badoo, but are more dating platforms, which narrows their usage. Users there can connect from a long distance. Mentioned platforms do not allow subscribing, which is offered by Instagram, but getting followers there takes a lot of time and budget.
INSTINCTY is a social media platform, that has interesting and unique functions and offers a different direction. Unlike big companies, we can create more opportunities and offer comfortable tools, such as high-quality photo uploads, the ability to gain subscribers in a short time, etc.

                    </p>
