                    <p class="col-md-10">
                        INSTINCTY needs so-called ‘back-end development’ to get a wide market share, which will take approximately one month. After this, an intensive promoting and platform development process can start.
During a certain period, ads for INSTINCTY should be shown frequently in multiple places.
Using digital marketing, video ads and download links will be shown to a specific segment on different social media platforms. INSTINCTY can also be advertised by influencers, by offering them specific benefits on the platform. 
INSTINCTY is a platform that is dependent on the number of its users. Because of this, on the launch date and the start of the intense marketing, an entertaining game can be offered to users, giving them a specific prize.
For example: when you download an application, clues are offered. By guessing them, you end up at specific locations, e.g shops, educational institutions, etc. This will help promote chosen locations and give INSTINCTY additional resources. A game will help users to get to know platforms' boundless possibilities and help the platform to gain an audience.

                    </p>
