                    <h2>Sustainability</h2>
                    <p class="col-md-10">
                        INSTINCTY will not be geographically restricted. After establishing in Georgia, we plan to register citizens of other countries on the platform. Similar activities will be planned to gain a market share in other countries too (supposedly, after a year). But before that, the grant will help us to test the platform’s abilities in Georgia, improve INSTINCTY and receive additional income from different companies, from which some already are our partners, and finally, proudly present INSTINCTY on a global market.
Our application offers 3 ways of making a profit, but additional sources can be added in the future:
1.Promotion of partners and their products, helping them in the realization process (for example, we can offer companies a place on the map, from which the users will be able to view their profile and subscribe to them).
The target audience – Users who are close to the locations of the competitors, and/or the locations of our partners, will receive offers/discounts even when they are offline. Prices of these kinds of messages will be specific, like on other social media platforms, people are charged for potential clients.
2.Charging for additional features (for example, getting pinned on a specific location, or a specific color, drawing on a profile)
3.Income received from Tokenization.

